{"tid":662854,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【食住個勢】御半山加推98伙 平均實呎15947元","createTime":"2018-05-12T18:53:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T01:43:24.000Z","uid":68476,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4ac6d7cf7132d679050d2a02768dab5bd5ba17bb","tid":662854,"uid":68476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T18:53:06.000Z","msg":"【食住個勢】御半山加推98伙 平均實呎15947元<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20180512/s00011/4c1da0b6b920b313bf870f2d6bd034d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20180512%2Fs00011%2F4c1da0b6b920b313bf870f2d6bd034d8.jpg&h=c40aebe3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新地（0016）屯門御半山沽清首批188個單位後，發展商即日加推3號價單，涉及98個單位，包括16伙1房、26伙1房連儲物室、50伙2房及6伙2房單位連儲物室，平均實呎20186元，折實平均實呎則為15947元，比本月3日首張價單折實平均實呎15248元略高4.5%，部份單位加價約3至5%。"},{"pid":"658f664192b4d18e010392f7c9338b22a2c7f2c2","tid":662854,"uid":59567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T01:43:24.000Z","msg":"大灣區中心去深圳只需30分鐘有乜理由咁平？"}]}